com.mumfrey.liteloader.client.gui.modlist

Class ModListEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mumfrey.liteloader.client.gui.modlist.ModListEntry

  • public class ModListEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a mod in the mod info screen, keeps track of mod information and provides methods for displaying the mod in the mod list and drawing the selected mod info.
    Author:
    Adam Mummery-Smith
